+## 6) Active Faculty Calendar Surface
+
+- Where it appears: `src/system-admin-live-app.tsx`, `src/system-admin-faculty-calendar-workspace.tsx`, `src/api/client.ts`, `src/pages/calendar-pages.tsx`
